    "collapsible_content_99xGkn": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_nKAUWj": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can the Honiture T10 effectively handle and manage cleaning in complex or multi-story homes?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>T10 uses advanced <strong>LiDAR navigation<\/strong> for precise and rapid mapping. It supports creating and storing <strong>up to 5 editable floor plans<\/strong>. This is highly beneficial for users with multi-story homes<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_gJPACx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is the Honiture T10 suction powerful enough to clean carpets and pet hair thoroughly?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>T10 boasts a leading <strong>6000Pa ultra-strong suction<\/strong>, sufficient for deep cleaning tasks.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_fQqen9": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What about Honiture T10 battery life and maintenance costs?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The T10 runs for up to 120 minutes per charge and automatically returns to recharge. Its 250 ml dustbin and 300 ml water tank are adequate for small-to-medium homes but may need frequent emptying in larger spaces. <\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_LBe8fD": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I prevent the robot from entering certain areas (e.g., bathroom or pet feeding station)?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Users can easily set up <strong>virtual No-Go Zones<\/strong> via the App to designate areas the T10 should avoid. Combined with its <strong>smart obstacle avoidance sensors<\/strong>, this ensures highly customized and safe cleaning, preventing collisions and falls.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_GWMXB9": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is the Honiture T10 compatible with smart home systems and voice assistants?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes. It connects via 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi and supports remote control through the Honiture App. It also works with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant for hands-free operation. Make sure your router is set to a 2.4 GHz network during setup.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
